<procdesc>The feature class structure has changed in IWEBDB (NRM Production) ALP_Rnn.RECORDBOUNDARY feature class. Columns have been added and deleted. This request is to update the published SMABoundary feature class to align to those changes. We have already prepared a feature class to use for the update in EDW: S_STAGE_LAND.EDW_SMABOUNDARY_STAGING. The weekly refresh/publication process already points to the S_STAGE_LAND.EDW_SMABOUNDARY_STAGING to update the records weekly. Now the S_USA.SMABoundary feature class structure needs to be updated to match it. The metadata and FS GIS Data Dictionary needs to be updated. Information for metadata and dictionary changes can be obtained from the Production feature class IWEBDB ALP_Rnn.RECORDBOUNDARY metadata: https://usfs.box.com/v/LSRSDDProdRecordBoundary. These changes will also affect layerfiles that EDW staff maintain: BoundarySurvey_SMA_SurfaceManagementArea_Boundary_EDW.lyr 
